---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout>

<h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900">About Bright Horizon</h1>

<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-12">
  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">Our Story</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Founded with a clear vision: to help businesses thrive in the digital age. Bright Horizon emerged from a passion for creating exceptional digital solutions that drive real business results.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      What started as a small development team has grown into a trusted partner for businesses across industries, from ambitious startups to established enterprises.
    </p>
  </div>
  
  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">Our Mission</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      We believe in the transformative power of technology. Our mission is to empower businesses with digital solutions that are not just technically sound, but also strategically aligned with their goals.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      Every project, every code line, and every design decision is made with one goal in mind: helping our clients succeed.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-blue-50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-blue-100">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900">Our Values</h2>
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <div>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-blue-600">Excellence</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700">We maintain the highest standards in everything we do, from code quality to customer service.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-blue-600">Innovation</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700">We stay ahead of industry trends and leverage cutting-edge technologies to deliver competitive advantages.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-blue-600">Partnership</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700">Your success is our success. We work as an extension of your team with transparency and collaboration.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</MainLayout>